<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer17394902583855613050">Walter Lord was an American author, best known for his documentary-style non-fiction account, <i>A Night to Remember</i>, about the sinking of the RMS <i>Titanic</i>.<br/><br/>In 2009, Jenny Lawrence edited and published <i>The Way It Was: Walter Lord on His Life and Books.</i></span>

</div>
